data.title: Wendhausen, Helmstedt Podcast
data.meta_description:
It is a village in the municipality of Lehre, in the district of Helmstedt, in Lower Saxony. Wendhausen is located about 10 km northeast of the center of Braunschweig. In terms of transportation, Wendhausen is connected to Braunschweig and Wolfsburg via the L 295.
